The lovely kitchen has custom cabinets w/crown molding, a walk-in pantry, a 5-burner stove, granite counters, an elevator in the foyer, and a custom fireplace; all bedrooms have walk-in closets.
The outside guest room for Casita has a bathroom with 440SF
The balcony over the Ranch and the Henderson mountain
And one balcony looking at Las Vegas Blvd 
50k Credit to the buyer for closing cost/upgrade  
And 
25k to  buy the Rate down
